{"tid":148625,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【未及見父最後一面】杜惠東逝世一周年 杜如風：不孝女極度掛住你","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T11:39:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5af360cdee6a074e710455238089dc30d44e0f1","tid":148625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"樹欲靜而風不息&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n日本旅遊達人杜如風，平時玩的時候癲喪，食的時候豪放，到買的時候就更加瘋狂。<br />\n不過就算再玩得，面對摯親離世，都總會有哀傷悲痛之時。<br />\n去年今日，杜如風75歲父親杜惠東因腎衰竭去世，當時仍在大阪拍旅遊節目的杜如風，即趕返香港處理爸爸的喪事。之後再堅持返回拍攝崗位，但當時鏡頭前的杜如風，其中一隻眼，喊到連眼白都變成紅色&hellip;<br />\n一年過去，在生的人繼續為事業忙碌打併，但父親的忌日，杜如風怎會忘記，她今日在facebook留言，悼念她的父親：「今天是爸爸的死忌，轉眼就一年了...老實說，自己已經沒之前那麼傷心，因為我知道爸爸正在天堂樂得逍遙...但是...老豆...不孝女極度掛住你...時間越久，想念之情越來越深...子欲養而親不在的感覺實在令我很難受...!」  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170308/56401048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170308%2F56401048&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=7d378598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170308%2F56401048&h=e9185872\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170308/56401048</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170308/large/1488964656_0a32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170308%2Flarge%2F1488964656_0a32.jpg&h=0ea0d463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83d3cad39045ac6786bb0508f679710e115618c","tid":148625,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fc9a89acfaf4ce3a5b20ac6a49d86191d3551a","tid":148625,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"024558e31bb7f3fe6ca4c7dfb960a2b8431ac5ce","tid":148625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"你知道佢既歷史後 <br />\n就明白,佢係正宗香港公主 <br />\n唔係公主病,而係伸隻手出黎有人埋單 <br />\n話今日好悶就會有10個男仔渣車係樓下等 <br />\n放工會有仔渣車搶頭淡湯等 <br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都唔知佢乜來頭 <br />\n就算80後都未必人人知 <br />\n但知道既會覺得佢係好傳奇 <br />\n根本係公主既教母"},{"pid":"c150461118c428f77e3e4b309bf5821d11096e70","tid":148625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d94d1cc471ac8dd7bf142008161b9e4b50d3fb","tid":148625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9709622c7207cac3fbb5d969a9c03c65626fd7c7","tid":148625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}